(*
This proof is quite complicated:
* The invertibles of monoid form a group.
* For a finite group, finite_group_Fermat |- !g a. FiniteGroup g /\ a IN G ==> (a ** CARD G = #e)
* Thus   a ** (CARD G - 1) = |/ a
